title: Cook Dark Skin Tone
description: A person with a dark skin tone wearing a chef's hat and apron, often seen in a kitchen setting. Represents cooking, culinary arts, and food preparation.
apple_vendor_description: The cook emoji on Apple devices presents a person with a warm, inviting dark skin tone, wearing a crisp white chef's hat and a matching apron. Their expression is one of focused enthusiasm, with a slight smile and bright eyes, suggesting a passion for culinary arts. Rendered with Apple's characteristic smooth gradients and soft rounded edges, this emoji on Apple devices embodies skill, delicious food, and the joy of cooking.
